    </head>
    <body>
        <div data-role="page" data-theme='b'>
            <%if !session[:uType].blank? && session[:uType] == "buyer" %>
				<%=render :partial => "my_deals/buyer_sub_menu" , :locals => {:header => "Jobs"}%>
			<%else -%>
				<%=render :partial => "my_deals/seller_sub_menu" , :locals => {:header => "Jobs"}%>
			<%end -%>
            <div data-role="content">
                <div data-role="collapsible-set" data-theme="b" data-content-theme="b">
                    <div data-role="collapsible" data-collapsed="false">
                        <h3>Jobs Home</h3>
                       		<div data-role="collapsible" data-collapsed="true">
                        		<h3>Post a Job</h3>
                        		<ul data-role="listview">
                        			<li>
                        				As most employers believe that, it will be easier to post the jobs on the PC than mobile, we disabled this option at this time. We request you to post the jobs on the PC. You will see the matched profiles here on the mobile though. Thanks for understanding. For any questions, pleas write to support@mydeals247.com
                        			</li>
                        		</ul>
                        	</div>	
                        <div class='inset'>
                            <ul data-role="listview">
                                <li><a href="employer_jobs_posted">My Jobs Posted</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
